data.description: Selling As-Is. Welcome to this adorable Bungalow that is ready to be called yours. This 2 bedroom house features an open floor plan in the main living area, spacious bedrooms and closets, a lovely front porch where you can enjoy your morning coffee or tea, and a very spacious backyard! In the community of Osowatamie you can enjoy the Osowatamie Golf Course, Flint Hills Trail, which is great for walking, running and biking, and many other great amenities!
